On Tuesday, Tonto Dikeh, the controversial Nollywood actress, hinted on her desire to get a new set of boobs for her birthday which comes up on June 9.
The 33-year-old singer and mother of one with over 4 million followers on her Instagram made it known to the public through her instagram account (@tontolet ).
The philanthropist and self-acclaimed evangelist posted her thought in form of prayers to God.
“Dear Lord Jesus, I have all I want for now.
“My birthday wish is that you make my schedule and that of Dr Ayo align so I have my new boobs in Jesus name I pray!! Thanks in addy Lord
“ #KINGTONTO #KINGTONTOBIRTHDAYWISH #JUNE9TH #BUYING ME A NEW BREAST #BOOBSWISH #GEMINIBABY,’’ she wrote.
It is however believed that the new boobs she was talking about might be an additional plaster surgery to her mammary glans to enhance firmness.
In 2017, it was reported that the third child in the family of five had undergone plastic surgery twice in order to increase her butt size and also to enhance her body image.
